<page>
   <topic>ARRAY.CLEAR Function</topic>
   <syntax>V Clear([N start[,N end]])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>start</name>
         <description>Numeric</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>end</name>
         <description>Numeric</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Clear the array.</description>
 
<discussion><![CDATA[The <ARRAY>.CLEAR() method clears the contents of a single dimensional array. The optional Start and End arguments restrict the portion of the array that is cleared out.
]]>
</discussion> 

