<section>
<description><![CDATA[To remove blank entries from an array, use the <ARRAY>.DELETE() method and the <ARRAY>.INITIALIZE() method. For example:]]></description>
<example><![CDATA[
Temp = A.DUMP()
A.clear(1, A.SIZE())
A.INITIALIZE(Temp)
]]></example>
